[b]TVO Big Ideas, November 8, 2008: Ronald Wright on American identity[/b]

Ronald Wright, the author of [i]What Is America?: A Short History of the New World Order[/i], examines the dichotomy between &quot;America's ideals and the realities&quot;. Wright discusses how such conflicts as those between Native Americans and the Europeans who came to settle the new world have shaped the American identity.

